headline: Lynn Good Elected to Morgan Stanley Board of Directors
summary: NEW YORK, June 16, 2025--Morgan Stanley (NYSE: MS) today announced that Lynn Good has been elected to the Company’s Board of Directors, effective July 18, 2025.
